# OCC Converse API — Complete Codebase Knowledge Guide

> Simple language. Real examples. Everything explained from scratch.

---

## 🧠 What Is This App? (30-second version)

**It's a chatbot for IndiGo airline crew.**

When a pilot or cabin crew member has a problem — "where is my hotel?", "I need a cab", "I want a day off" — they open this chat app and type their question.

The bot reads their question, understands what they need, checks their roster data, and replies with the right answer or escalates to a human agent.

---

## 👤 Who Uses It?

| User | What they do |
|---|---|
| **Crew Member (Pilot / Cabin)** | Asks questions about hotel, transport, lounge, duty travel, sick leave, day off |
| **OCC Operator** | Monitors chats, handles transfers, sees flight/crew overview |
| **Admin** | Manages knowledge base (policy PDFs), vector store |

