## 🏗️ BACKEND — Deep Dive

### `app/main.py` — The Entry Point

This is where the server starts. Think of it as the front door.

```python
app = FastAPI(title="crewBot")
app.add_middleware(CORSMiddleware, ...)   # Allow frontend to call backend
app.include_router(api_router)           # Register all routes
```

On startup it:
1. Configures logging
2. Creates MongoDB indexes for fast session lookup

