#### All API Endpoints

| Method | URL | What it does |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/health` | Is the server alive? |
| `GET` | `/userinfo` | List available test crew profiles |
| `POST` | `/userinfo` | Login as a crew member → creates session |
| `POST` | `/userinfo/guest` | Start anonymous session (collects email via chat) |
| `POST` | `/chat` | **Main endpoint** — send a message, get a reply |
| `POST` | `/chat` (bootstrap) | Load roster data → streams welcome + roster messages |
