| `GET` | `/session/list` | List all sessions for an email |
| `POST` | `/session/roster-bootstrap` | Load crew's roster from Crew Mobile API |
| `POST` | `/vectorstore/crewcontrol` | Ingest policy PDFs into vector store (crew control) |
| `POST` | `/vectorstore/crewlogistics` | Ingest policy PDFs into vector store (logistics) |

