#### How a Message Gets Processed (Step by Step)

```
Crew sends: "Where is my hotel?"
                │
                ▼
         POST /chat
                │
                ▼
         ChatService.handle_message()
                │
                ▼
         OrchestratorService.handle()
         ┌──────────────────────────┐
         │                          │
         │  Step 1: GPT-1           │  ← "What does crew want?"
         │  → Intent: "hotel"       │     Classifies intent
         │  → Workflow: ["hotel"]   │     Returns JSON decision
         │                          │
         │  Step 2: WorkflowExecutor│  ← Runs the hotel workflow
         │  → Checks crew auth      │     Checks hours since arrival
         │  → Checks hotel data     │     Decides: ticket / transfer / info
         │  → Returns decision      │
         │                          │
         │  Step 3: GPT-2           │  ← "How should we say this?"
         │  → Formats human reply   │     Turns decision into natural text
         │                          │
         └──────────────────────────┘
                │
                ▼
         JSON response → Frontend → Crew sees reply
```

