##### Workflow: Crew Logistics (the biggest one)

```
Crew asks about a logistics topic
            │
            ▼
    LogisticsWorkflow
            │
     ┌──────┴──────┐
     │             │
     ▼             ▼
  Level 1        Level 2
  (main menu)    (sub-flows)
     │
     ├── Duty Travel (DHT/DHF detection, PNR check, time window)
     ├── Seat Assignment (seat shown / defer to airport / not applicable)
     ├── Excess Baggage (10kg/30kg/100kg/150kg policy by duty code + rank)
     ├── Change in Booking (routes to Crew Training / Pilot Admin / IFS Admin)
     ├── Unable to Reach for Flight (asks reason → transfers)
     ├── Issue at Check-in (immediate transfer)
     ├── Reimbursement (create ticket)
     └── Feedback (create ticket)
