##### Workflow: Hotel

```
Crew asks about hotel
        │
        ├── No hotel assigned?
        │   ├── Arrived < 2h → Transfer to agent
        │   ├── Next duty < 12h → Create ticket
        │   └── International?
        │       ├── Halt < 4h → Not authorised
        │       └── Halt ≥ 4h → Forex card message
        │
        ├── Day Use request?
        │   ├── Halt < 4h → Not authorised (regardless of crew type)
        │   └── Halt ≥ 4h + Operating crew → App link
        │
        ├── Hotel Cab?
        │   ├── Airport → Hotel → Ask if contacted hotel first
        │   └── Hotel → Airport/Training → Transfer / Create ticket
        │
        ├── Issue in room? → 9 issue types → Collect details → Transfer
        ├── Stay Extension → Create ticket
        ├── Relocation → Ticket (+ IFS approval if Cabin)
        ├── Feedback → URL form (Cockpit) or Ticket (Cabin)
        └── Reimbursement → Create ticket
```

---

##### Workflow: Lounge

```
Crew asks about lounge access
        │
        ├── Q1: International station? → Forex card message (exit)
        ├── Q2: Halt < 2h? → Not eligible (exit)
        ├── Q3: Training/Ground duty? → Not eligible (exit)
        ├── Q4: No contracted lounge + halt 2-4h? → INR 500 meal (exit)
        ├── Q5: Special station + next leg international? → INR 500 (exit)
        ├── Q6: Halt 3h-12h + Operating + no lounge? → Auth email (exit)
        │
        └── Awaiting in lounge? (A-paths)
            ├── A1: Within 3h + lounge operational → Transfer to agent
            ├── A2: Special station + INTL next leg → INR 500
            ├── A3: DEL3/CCJ + domestic next leg → Transfer
            ├── A4: No lounge + within 3h → INR 500
            ├── A5: Lounge not operational → Show hours + INR 500
            ├── A6: Outside 3h-12h → Auth email
            └── A7: Outside 12h → Auth email / INR 500

C-paths: Couldn't use lounge → Create P2 ticket
S-paths: Had lounge issue → INR 500 + ticket / Acknowledge
R-paths: Reimbursement/Feedback → Collect details → Create ticket
```

