##### Workflow: Bluepoint (Day Off)

```
Crew asks for a day off
        │
        ├── validate_date() → Filter roster to eligible dates
        ├── apply_bluepoint_dayoff()
        │   ├── Selected today → TODAY_OFF constant (transfer to live agent)
        │   ├── Selected future date → NEXT_DAY_OFF.format(date) (create ticket)
        │   └── Invalid date → "not available for day off selection"
        └── get_dayoff_valid_dates() → Calls MCP roster (async)
```

