## 🔐 Security & Auth

| What | How |
|---|---|
| Crew identity | `staff_id` / `iga_code` validated on every request before any logic runs |
| No real DB in tests | In-memory repo replaces MongoDB entirely |
| No real AI in tests | `StubChatService` returns deterministic replies |
| No secrets in CI | Fake env values used everywhere |
| Prompt injection | Tested: bot refuses "ignore previous instructions" attacks |
| Data leakage | Tested: bot never echoes secret tokens back |
| Authority bypass | Tested: "approved by admin" in message doesn't skip confirmation step |

